Invocation Name: get me a buzzword
des:
If you need a buzzword to help you in a meeting - this skill has your back!
It picks a random word from a whole set of Agile related buzzwords for you to use.
Alternatively, if you want some words to try and use in a meeting for a bit of a laugh, this'll also do the job.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
